0.1.name: wordpress/feed-geomashup
0.1.description: FeedGeoMashup lets FeedWordPress pass GeoRSS data to GeoMashup. Starting with v2.0 you will find plugin options integrated into the FeedWordPress Admin UI. In particlar, you can set site-wide and feed-specific preferences to filter out posts that do not include GeoRSS data. You must have installed, activated and configured both FeedWordPress and GeoMashup.
